title: The Last of Russ
description:
Nate Tice of The Athletic helps Mina process all of her thoughts and feelings on the Russell Wilson trade. Plus, they discuss potential landing spots for Jordan Love, the ramifications of Calvin Ridley's suspension, and combine standouts.
